# ── AQML Language Recognition ──────────────────────────────
# Tells GitHub Linguist to treat .aqml files as YAML-derivative
# with syntax highlighting. Until AQML is added to Linguist's
# languages.yml, this ensures proper display on GitHub.

*.aqml linguist-language=YAML
*.aqml linguist-detectable=true

# ── Standard ──────────────────────────────────────────────
*.md linguist-documentation
LICENSE linguist-documentation
